 Copies of this publication are for sale by the National Technical Information Service, U.S. Department of Commerce,
Springfield, VA 22161. When ordering, refer to Federal Information Processing Standards Publication XX (FIPS PUB
XX), and identify the title. When microfiche is desired, this should be specified. Prices are published by NTIS in
current catalogs and other issuances. Payment may be made by check, money order, deposit account or charged to a credit
